          <p class="text-sm mb-3 text-secondary">Founder & Director</p>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-text">With over two decades of experience in contemporary art curation, Dr. Chen has organized exhibitions at major institutions across Asia, Europe, and North America. Her research focuses on cross-cultural artistic exchange and the role of art in global discourse.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="aspect-square w-32 gradient-placeholder-3 mb-4"></div>
