          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-text">Sarah Lin brings extensive experience in contemporary Asian art, having previously held curatorial positions at the Shanghai Museum of Contemporary Art and the Mori Art Museum in Tokyo. She specializes in emerging artistic practices and new media.</p>
